<div class="container" style="margin-top:40px;">

<h1>Refund Policy</h1>

<p>
SupportX follows a transparent refund policy 
to ensure donor satisfaction.
</p>

<h3>Refund Eligibility</h3>

<ul>
<li>If payment was made by mistake</li>
<li>If duplicate payment occurred</li>
<li>If technical error caused incorrect payment</li>
</ul>

<h3>Refund Request Process</h3>

<p>
To request a refund, users must contact 
SupportX within <strong>7 days</strong> of payment.
</p>

<h3>Refund Method</h3>

<p>
Approved refunds will be processed 
to the original payment method 
within 5–7 working days.
</p>

<h3>Non-Refundable Cases</h3>

<ul>
<li>Voluntary donations already processed</li>
<li>Requests made after 7 days</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 2026</p>

</div>

